          "order": 1,
          "title": "MILLION",
          "summary": "Million.js is a virtual DOM library that speeds up rendering in React components. It reduces the overhead of the React Reconciler by using an optimized virtual DOM. Million.js can be used inside React and is much faster than Preact. It makes it easy to create user interfaces with fast rendering and load speeds.",
