          "order": 2,
          "title": "CSS MASKING",
          "summary": "Masking is a popular technique in design that is rarely used in web design due to limited browser support. CSS masking is slated to be part of Interop 2023, allowing for cross-browser support. This article looks at the basics of CSS masking and provides examples of how designers can utilize it.",
